=\n| caption=\n| pronun=\n| othernames=\n| titles=[[Ruling Steward]]\n| position=\n| location=\n| affiliation=\n| language=\n| birth={{TA|2700}}\n| birthlocation=\n| rule={{TA|2763}} - {{TA|2811|n}} (48 years)\n| death={{TA|2811}}\n| deathlocation=\n| age=111\n| notablefor=\n| house=[[House of Húrin]]\n| parentage=[[Beren (Steward of Gondor)|Beren]]\n| siblings=\n| spouse=\n| children=[[Belecthor II]]\n| gender=Male\n| height=\n| hair=\n| eyes=\n| clothing=\n| weapons=\n| steed=\n}}'''Beregond''' ([[Third Age]] 2700<ref name=\":0\">{{PM|Elendil}}, p. 205</ref> – 2811,<ref name=\"South\">{{App|South}}</ref> aged 111 years) was the twentieth Ruling Steward of [[Gondor]].  \n\n==History==\nBeregond was born the third child of his father [[Beren (Steward of Gondor)|Beren]].<ref name=\":0\" />\n\nBeregond was the greatest captain since the time of [[Boromir (Steward of Gondor)|Boromir]]. Before the spring of {{TA|2759}} Beregond defeated the [[Corsairs of Umbar]], who had invaded the [[Outlands|southern coasts]] of Gondor. Then he was able to send help to the [[Rohirrim]], who had been attacked by a combined force of [[Dunlendings]] and [[Corsairs of Umbar|Corsairs]] that had sailed up the [[Isen]].\n\nHe succeeded his father [[Beren (Steward of Gondor)|Beren]] at his death in {{TA|2763|n}}. By this time Gondor started recovering its strength.\n\nDuring Beregond's rule, the [[War of the Dwarves and Orcs]] was fought ({{TA|2793}} - {{TA|2799|n}}).  Only rumours of the fighting came south until Orcs fleeing from the [[Battle of Nanduhirion]] crossed [[Rohan]] and established themselves in the [[White Mountains]].  Fighting occurred in many dales before they were eradicated.<ref>{{App|Stewards}}</ref>\n\nBeregond was followed by his son [[Belecthor II]] at his death in 2811.<ref name=\"South\" />\n\n==Genealogy==\n{{familytree/start}}\n{{familytree | EGA |EGA=[[Egalmoth (Steward of Gondor)|Egalmoth]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2626|n}} - {{TA|2743|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | BER |BER=[[Beren (Steward of Gondor)|Beren]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2655|n}} - {{TA|2763|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | BER |BER='''BEREGOND'''<br/><small>''{{TA|2700|n}} - {{TA|2811|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | BEL |BEL=[[Belecthor II]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2752|n}} - {{TA|2872|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | THO |THO=[[Thorondir]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2782|n}} - {{TA|2882|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree/end}}\n\n{{References}}\n{{seq-start}}\n{{seq-head\n| race=gondorian\n| house=[[House of Húrin]]\n| born={{TA|2700}}\n| died={{TA|2811}}\n}}\n{{seq\n| prev=[[Beren (Steward of Gondor)|Beren]]\n| list=20th [[Ruling Steward|Ruling Steward of Gondor]]\n| dates={{TA|2763}} – {{TA|2811|n}}\n| next=[[Belecthor II]]\n}}\n{{seq-end}}\n{{rulingstewards}}\n{{title}}\n[[Category:Gondorians]]\n[[Category:House of Húrin]]\n[[Category:Ruling stewards]]\n[[Category:Third Age characters]]\n\n[[de:Beregond (Truchsess von Gondor)]]\n[[fi:Beregond (käskynhaltija)]]\n[[fr:encyclo:personnages:hommes:3a:dunedain:gondoriens:beregond i]]"}}}